divs: Sighting Detailsit was thanksgiving day at 12.10 pm i stoped my car in my drive. i looked up before i got out'' then i saw, a siv''cigar seting in midair. like a blimp. and 750 ft. above. it had long dark braches coming out of it. i watched for over 1 min,, know sound at all. i put my car in park then looked up and it was right close,, 200 ft or less above me. i got out of the car but it was long gone. i didn;t lose any time but it took me 6 hr;s to rem'' that it happened.
